          <h2 class="card-title">
            Introduction
          </h2>
          <p class="card-text">
            Okay, now you’re reading the long version. This is the privacy policy for Sir Stratalot—the website you’re looking at. Sir Stratalot is operated by We Are The Holograms Inc. This policy explains what personal data this website collects, how we use it, and your rights regarding that data. If you have questions about this policy or how Sir Stratalot handles your personal data, you can reach us with the <a href="#contact">contact information</a> provided at the end of this policy.
          </p>
        </div>
