        <div class="card-body">
          <div id="dataprocessors" class="anchor"></div>
          <h2 class="card-title">
            Disclosure of personal data to third parties & data processors
          </h2>
          <p class="card-text">
            We may disclose personal data to:
          </p>
          <ul class="card-text">
            <li>third party service providers for the purpose of enabling them to provide their services, including (without limitation) IT service providers, data storage, hosting and server providers, ad networks, analytics, error loggers, debt collectors, maintenance or problem-solving providers, marketing or advertising providers, professional advisors and payment systems operators; and</li>
            <li>third parties to collect and process data.</li>
          </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="card-text">
            Sir Stratalot uses the following data processors with personal data we collect from you:
          </p>
          <ul class="card-text">
            <li><a href="https://www.heroku.com" target="_blank">Heroku</a> is a cloud platform for hosting apps and websites; they host Sir Stratalot and all server log data and analytics. Heroku is owned by Salesforce. <a href="https://www.salesforce.com/company/privacy" target="_blank">Salesforce Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://mlab.com/" target="_blank">mLab</a> provides database storage and services. If you create a Sir Stratalot account by signing in with Twitter, your account data is stored with mLab. <a href="https://mlab.com/company/legal/privacy" target="_blank">mLab Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.google.com/analytics" target="_blank">Google Analytics</a> provides anonymized data concerning site visitors and activity at the website. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Analytics Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
